{"tid":560435,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"午飯時間！速睇邊間人氣餐廳「最唔健康」","createTime":"2018-02-14T05:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T22:09:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"075fbe0f3473e063897cdc8b6eea49a7e8165f51","tid":560435,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:55:17.000Z","msg":"又夠鐘食午餐！日本拉麵、雲南米線、雲吞麵都係唔少上班一族的午飯首選。消委會與食安中心合作，測試本地食肆所售的100款非預先包裝亞洲風味湯粉麵的鈉含量，當中包含10種亞洲湯粉麵。 <br />\n<br />\n世衞建議成人每日的鈉攝取量不應多於2000毫克，食物安全中心表示，當人體的鈉水平偏高時，會在尿液排出多餘的鈉，若未能排出足夠的鈉，往往會積存體內，因而可能引致高血壓。有些人對鈉較為敏感，即他們會較易貯存鈉，因而可能增加患上高血壓的風險。 <br />\n<br />\n到底你平時最愛的人氣餐廳係咪「榜上有名」？一圖睇晒！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180214/photo/bkn-20180214131024743-0214_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180214135105\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180214131024743-0214_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180214135105&h=0b56354a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180214/bkn-20180214131024743-0214_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180214%2Fbkn-20180214131024743-0214_00822_001.html&d=rwA%2B5pHQ3r474X4t2NstPLZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=8a484d1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180214/bkn-20180214131024743-0214_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bf48a616537afba95d62f28030538d831254e80f","tid":560435,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:56:29.000Z","msg":"D人食完仲話飲埋碗味精湯"},{"pid":"f8ac9a8f7f531679dc484f071e8183966e5ea51d","tid":560435,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T22:09:00.000Z","msg":"Hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}